OL,6,FThe month of Ramadan has arrived and
OL,7,FMuslim communities will be preparing
OL,8,Ffor a period of fasting.
OL,10,FDuring Ramadan, Muslims refrain from
OL,11,Feating, drinking, smoking, and sexual
OL,12,Fintercourse from sunrise until
OL,13,Fsunset. Even a tiny sip of water or a
OL,14,Fpuff of smoke is enough to invalidate
OL,15,Fthe fast. At night, family and
OL,16,Ffriends gather and feast in a festive
OL,17,Fatmosphere.
